Use Case: ExportLog
Short description: This usecase is initiated when the user presses the Export Log button. A txt file will be exported with the content of the current log.

Priority: Medium

Extends or Includes: UC_Harvester

Participating actors: User, Harvester

Normal flow of events:

User                                    System
----                                    ------
User clicks Stop Parser button

								
					Harvester stops parsing.

Goto UC_Harvester

